--- EAI_AGAIN
--- EAI_BADFLAGS
--- EAI_BADHINTS
--- EAI_FAIL
--- EAI_FAMILY
--- EAI_MAX
--- EAI_MEMORY
--- EAI_NODATA
--- EAI_NONAME
--- EAI_PROTOCOL
--- EAI_SERVICE
--- EAI_SOCKTYPE
--- EAI_SYSTEM

[[m:Socket.getaddrinfo]]が失敗したときに返すエラーコードです。
[[man:getaddrinfo(3)]]も参照して下さい。

